http://www.birt-exchange.com/devshare/designing-birt-reports/412-change-birt-chart-interval-type-at-runtime/

Report Design that changes chart interval with script

This example report design uses script in the beforeFactory event to change the chart interval type from Days, Weeks, Months, and Years at runtime based on a user parameter.

This example was created wtih BIRT 2.2.0 and uses the sample ClassicModels database.